title: U S  stocks lower at close of trade  Dow Jones Industrial Average down 0 50
content:
Investing com   U S  stocks were lower after the close on Monday  as losses in the Oil   Gas  Basic Materials and Financials sectors led shares lower 
At the close in NYSE  the Dow Jones Industrial Average declined 0 50   while the S P 500 index declined 0 40   and the NASDAQ Composite index lost 0 25  
The best performers of the session on the Dow Jones Industrial Average were Merck   Company Inc  NYSE MRK   which rose 1 00  or 0 66 points to trade at 66 73 at the close  Meanwhile  Apple Inc  NASDAQ AAPL  added 0 65  or 1 34 points to end at 208 87 and  Visa Inc   NYSE V  was up 0 34  or 0 48 points to 140 21 in late trade 
The worst performers of the session were DowDuPont Inc  NYSE DWDP   which fell 1 74  or 1 18 points to trade at 66 56 at the close  JPMorgan Chase   Co  NYSE JPM  declined 1 58  or 1 83 points to end at 113 90 and International Business Machines  NYSE IBM  was down 1 23  or 1 77 points to 142 71 
The top performers on the S P 500 were Nielsen Holdings  NYSE NLSN  which rose 12 02  to 24 61  Sysco Corporation  NYSE SYY  which was up 6 22  to settle at 72 74 and News Corp B  NASDAQ NWS  which gained 3 72  to close at 13 95 
The worst performers were  Lennar  Corporation  NYSE LEN  which was down 4 87  to 50 78 in late trade  Chesapeake Energy Corporation  NYSE CHK  which lost 4 61  to settle at 4 445 and Harley Davidson Inc  NYSE HOG  which was down 4 35  to 41 37 at the close 
The top performers on the NASDAQ Composite were ReShape Lifesciences Inc  NASDAQ RSLS  which rose 38 00  to 0 1311  Ability Inc  NASDAQ ABIL  which was up 30 22  to settle at 5 99 and  iFresh Inc   NASDAQ IFMK  which gained 29 25  to close at 3 80 
The worst performers were Sphere 3D Corp  NASDAQ ANY  which was down 32 43  to 0 205 in late trade  Determine Inc  NASDAQ DTRM  which lost 21 89  to settle at 0 929 and  Broadway Financial  Corporation  NASDAQ BYFC  which was down 20 32  to 1 490 at the close 
Falling stocks outnumbered advancing ones on the New York Stock Exchange by 2042 to 1029 and 41 ended unchanged  on the Nasdaq Stock Exchange  1625 fell and 939 advanced  while 141 ended unchanged 
Shares in Sysco Corporation  NYSE SYY  rose to all time highs  up 6 22  or 4 26 to 72 74  Shares in Merck   Company Inc  NYSE MRK  rose to 5 year highs  rising 1 00  or 0 66 to 66 73  Shares in Sphere 3D Corp  NASDAQ ANY  fell to all time lows  losing 32 43  or 0 098 to 0 205  Shares in Determine Inc  NASDAQ DTRM  fell to all time lows  losing 21 89  or 0 261 to 0 929  Shares in Broadway Financial Corporation  NASDAQ BYFC  fell to 52 week lows  losing 20 32  or 0 380 to 1 490  
The CBOE Volatility Index  which measures the implied volatility of S P 500 options  was up 12 16  to 14 76 a new 1 month high 
Gold Futures for December delivery was down 1 50  or 18 30 to  1200 70 a troy ounce  Elsewhere in commodities trading  Crude oil for delivery in September fell 0 44  or 0 30 to hit  67 33 a barrel  while the October Brent oil contract fell 0 05  or 0 04 to trade at  72 77 a barrel
